Preparation
1. Install ruby 1.8.x

2. Clone PatternSearch source from github

3. Install rubytree with dependecy
	gem install rubytree

4. Install stanfordparser
	gem install stanfordparser
	Download and copy englishPCFG.ser.gz, stanford-parser.jar to
		# UNIX:: /usr/local/stanford-parser/current
		# Windows:: C:\stanford-parser\current
		from http://nlp.stanford.edu/software/stanford-parser-2008-10-26.tgz

5. Install rjb
	gem install rjb

6. Install treebank
	gem install treebank

7. Setup jdk
	Install jdk
	set environment variable JAVA_HOME to C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_xx

9. Setup Solr
	Download solr from http://apache.tt.co.kr/lucene/solr/1.3.0/apache-solr-1.3.0.zip
	Configure solr server
		copy scheme.xml
	Start solr server
		cd {solr root}/example
		java -jar start.jar
		http://localhost:8983/solr/admin/

8. Install solr-ruby gem
	gem install solr-ruby


9. Do rake to test!